Description: Smart multi-service Docker builder with advanced Git change detection
  Dockerz v2.75.0 is a powerful CLI tool for building and pushing multiple Docker
  images in parallel with advanced smart features and comprehensive Git operation
  support. It supports intelligent change detection, multi-level caching, smart
  build orchestration, and robust handling of complex Git scenarios to significantly
  improve CI/CD pipeline performance.
  .
  Features include:
   - Advanced Git change detection (tags, branches, cherry-picks, resets)
   - Multi-level caching (layer, local hash, registry)
   - Smart build orchestration with service isolation
   - Enhanced logging and debugging capabilities
   - Automatic image name normalization
   - CI/CD integration with file-based interfaces
   - Google Artifact Registry support
   - Comprehensive Git operations handling
   - Robust error handling and stability

